データの可視化¶

量的変数と質的変数を分ける関数を作成¶

In [9]:
def numlist(df):
    numberlist = []
    d = dict(df.dtypes)
    for i in d.keys():
        if d[i] != 'object':
            numberlist.append(i)
    df_num = df.loc[:,numberlist]
    return(df_num.head())


def objlist(df):
    objectlist = []
    d = dict(df.dtypes)
    for i in d.keys():
        if d[i] == 'object':
            objectlist.append(i)
    df_num = df.loc[:,objectlist]
    return(df_num.head())

欠損値があっても相関係数を算出する関数を作成¶

In [15]:
## 相関係数算出コード
import scipy as sp
# x,y にdf[???],df[???]のような形式で入れる
def corr_nun(x,y):
    # x,yの表を作成
    train_1_corr1=pd.concat([x,y],axis=1)
    # 合体させた表の欠損値を削除
    train_1_corr2=train_1_corr1.dropna()
    # 相関係数を算出
    corr=sp.stats.pearsonr(train_1_corr2.iloc[:,0],train_1_corr2.iloc[:,1])
    return(corr[0])

train_1_numlist=numlist(train_1)
for i in train_1_numlist.columns:
    var=i
    plt.scatter(train_1[var],train_1['SalePrice'])
    plt.xlabel(var)
    plt.ylabel('SalePrice')
    plt.title(corr_nun(train_1[var],train_1['SalePrice']))
    plt.show()

# カテゴリーデータについて、'SalePrice'との箱ひげ図を表示
train_1_objlist=objlist(train_1)
for i in train_1_objlist.columns:
    
    var =i
    data = pd.concat([train_1['SalePrice'], train_1[var]], axis=1)
    f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(20, 5))
    fig = sns.boxplot(x=var, y="SalePrice", data=data)
    fig.axis(ymin=0, ymax=800000)
